name: CountryJamz
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: country jams
des: Country Jamz, your gateway to the hottest country hits, now on the Alexa app! Immerse yourself in the heart of Nashville with our handpicked selection of chart-topping country tunes. From the latest hits to classic favorites, Country Jamz brings you the best in country music 24/7. What sets us apart? Our live DJs, true connoisseurs of country, who not only curate the perfect playlist but also share their expertise and passion for the genre. Experience the authenticity of country music with the voices that know it best. Tune in, turn up the twang, and let Country Jamz be your go-to destination for the ultimate country music experience on Alexa!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
